# Small Business Cybersecurity Checklist

## 🔐 Account Protection
- [ ] Use strong, unique passwords for all accounts
- [ ] Enable two-factor authentication (2FA) wherever possible
- [ ] Remove access from former employees immediately
- [ ] Use a password manager for storing credentials

## 🖥️ Device Security
- [ ] Install antivirus and anti-malware software
- [ ] Keep all operating systems and software up to date
- [ ] Encrypt all business laptops and phones
- [ ] Require screen locks with timeouts

## ☁️ Data & Cloud Services
- [ ] Back up critical data regularly (preferably to the cloud)
- [ ] Restrict access to sensitive files based on roles
- [ ] Use secure file-sharing services

## 🧾 Basic Policies & Training
- [ ] Create and share an Acceptable Use Policy (AUP)
- [ ] Train employees on phishing and social engineering
- [ ] Conduct regular security reviews and audits
